Interface WatermarkTracker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LastWatermarkTracker, MultiWriterWatermarkTracker

    public interface WatermarkTracker
    An interface for a WatermarkTracker. Implementations are expected to serve as helper classes to track watermarks in different use-cases.
